{"tid":1834972,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"高鐵西九龍站出現退票人龍","createTime":"2020-01-22T15:44:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-23T03:45:36.000Z","uid":20933,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"9646ad16590624ecea028eb30314c21c5986ba23","tid":1834972,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T15:44:38.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】港鐵表示，會全面清潔消毒西九龍站的所有公眾地方，並已要求所有員工配戴口罩。有巿民表示，內地爆發疫情，寧願蝕錢亦決定取消行程。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵表示，已派人在患者在車站逗留過的範圍消毒。<br />\n<br />\n在西九龍站抵港層，有清潔人員用抹布清潔閘口，詢問處櫃枱就設置消毒洗手液機，並貼上告示。站內有廣播，指武漢出現新型肺炎確診個案，提醒旅客小心。<br />\n<br />\n不少乘客在大堂等候入閘，部分人亦有戴上口罩，站內職員全部都戴上口罩。<br />\n<br />\n有剛到埗的旅客表示，高鐵上有職員提醒加強清潔，不擔心疫情蔓延。有乘客擔心香港疫情蔓延，會盡量減少出門。<br />\n<br />\n西九龍站的櫃位，晚上出現退票人龍。有市民表示，高鐵密閉空間空氣不流通，寧願損失金錢。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵日前宣布，因應內地鐵路單位的退票安排，已經購買高鐵車票來往武漢的乘客，如需辦理退票，可以獲得全數退款。"},{"pid":"db4bf618e2f9907994838fae6797e4c7bae8520c","tid":1834972,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T15:44:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=377778\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D377778&d=UWp4lduD54HchuVgBglmzctxnk%2BhbBpP3j1S%2FgfPRD4%3D&h=869d4d71\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D377778&h=dcd31bc8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=377778</a>"},{"pid":"5dbb6258992f521b16390ef7c9db3f299091edee","tid":1834972,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T15:46:53.000Z","msg":"剩係得武漢退<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0162da893d792ba04a9fc63c72f162364de84a38","tid":1834972,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T15:48:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ca83a3833978c331726ff421495154bedfae3d6","tid":1834972,"uid":35598,"like":1,"dislike":